ENTRY            A0161   20260126   20260317   20260317       A129
SUBENT        A0161001   20260126   20260317   20260317       A129
BIB                 11         23
TITLE      Excitation function for the production of 123I
           via the 127I(p,5n)123Xe reaction
REFERENCE  (J,ARI,27,465,1976)
AUTHOR     (A.M.J.Paans,W.Vaalburg,G.Van HErk,M.G.Woldring)
INSTITUTE  (2NEDRUG)
FACILITY   (ISOCY,2NEDRUG)
SAMPLE     NaI target. Thickness= 1 MeV
           The NaI was pressed into an aluminium holder and
           tight sealed with an aluminium foil glued to the holder
METHOD     (SITA,EXTB,BCINT,ACTIV)
DETECTOR   (GELI) The Ge(Li) (35 cm3 with a FWHM of 3.8 keV
           at 1330 keV).
ADD-RES    (TTY-C)
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-T) Total error
           (ERR-S) Statistical error
           (ERR-1) The error of efficiency of detector
           (ERR-2) The error in the target thickness.
           (ERR-3) The errors in dead time correction
           and current integration.
HISTORY    (19820104C)
           (20090921A) BIB section updated.
           (20260126A) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
           DATA-ERR -> ERR-T.
ENDBIB              23
COMMON               5          3
ERR-S      ERR-1      ERR-2      ERR-3      EN-ERR-DIG
PER-CENT   PER-CENT   PER-CENT   PER-CENT   MEV
    5.        10.         5.         1.         0.25
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           30
